---
title: Quick Veggie Lentil Ziti-Style Pasta Bake with Basil and Ricotta
description: This quick veggie dinner is filled with cheesy tomato goodness! Though small in size, lentils are a nutritinal all-star in pasta. They are packed with fibre and protein. Enjoy this one-pan wonder!
